title: WordPress Plugin - USPS Shipping method for WooCommerce v2.1.8
description:
The USPS Shipping Method plugin for WooCommerce will get real-time rates from the UPS API. The plugin work with domestic and International package.



NEW Box Packing feature, add boxes and it will calculate which box and how much box to use

Rename default shipping name to suit your needs. With the included auto update, future updates will be available directly from Wordpress interface.
Domestic

   - Priority Mail
   - Express Mail
   - Standard Post
   - First-Class

International

  - Express Mail International
  - Priority Mail International
  - Global Express Guaranteed
  - First Class Package Service
